com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.frontend.cli
Class CommandParser

java.lang.Object
  com.csvanefalk.keytestgen.frontend.cli.CommandParser

public class CommandParser
extends java.lang.Object

Instances of this class are used in order to parse command line invocations of KeyTestGen2, both checking syntactical correctness and extracting user supplied data,

Author:
christopher

Constant Field Values

about

private boolean about
Set to display about information.

coverage

private final java.lang.String coverage
Select the degree of code coverage to guarantee. Only one option per session is legal. Default is standard statement coverage.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

files

private final java.util.List<java.lang.String> files
Select which Java files to use as a basis for test case generation.

help

private boolean help
Flag to decide if usage help should be shown.

methods

private final java.util.List<java.lang.String> methods
Select what methods to generate test cases for. This can either be done on a categorical basis (i.e. all, public, private, protected and/or native) or on a specific basis. Both ways can be combined in order to customize method coverage.

outputDirectory

private final java.lang.String outputDirectory
Select top-level output directory for the generated test suite(s). Default is the current directory at the time o invocation.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

testFrameworks

private final java.util.List<java.lang.String> testFrameworks
Select which test framework(s) to generate test cases for. Multiple selections are possible per session, in which case a separate output folder will be generated for each framework. Default is JUnit4.

verbose

private boolean verbose
Set to enable verbose mode.
